('98034','33827','5','Majorcan finca with character in Santa Maria'),
('98035','33828','5','This charming country house with lots of character sitting on a plot of 24 000m² and has a constructed area of 500m². The main house and guest house hosts 6 bedrooms, 5 bathrooms, 1 guest toilet, various seating areas and 2 kitchens. Furthermore this country house offers: central heating, own well, natural stone facade, large pool, various fruit trees, palmtrees, olive trees and vines. An evergreen subtropical garden with pergolas and several terraces of Marés stone with magnificent fountains, and a huge heated swimming pool and Jacuzzi with an exquisite pool house, round off the beautiful outdoor facilities. ATo  Palma de Mallorca is just 15 minutes drive'),
